title: Added a routine to handle problems with gcmIds which are not sync with the server
message:
Added a routine to handle problems with gcmIds which are not sync with the server

1. Check if regId and deviceId are on the server
- 1 found
- 2 only regId found
- 3 only deviceId found
- 4 nothing found
2. Take a look at the settings-> regId allready send?

1-1 -> do nothing, allright
1-2 -> update deviceID
1-3 -> update regId
2 / 1-4 -> send regId and deiceID to server

Added a deviceId to identify any device
